# How might we enhance financial literacy and access to microfinancing for rural women in India?

## Project Description
Rural women in India often lack access to financial services and education, affecting their ability to escape poverty and contribute to economic growth. This opportunity focuses on developing targeted financial literacy programs and microfinancing solutions that empower women to make informed financial decisions and improve their economic stability.


